PIM Multi-Topology ID (MT-ID) Join
Attribute
2011", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC6420.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document introduces a new type of PIM Join Attribute that extends PIM signaling to identify a topology that should be used when constructing a particular multicast distribution tree. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
